postcontent:
WTS Springfield Armory 1911-A1
 
First owner, genley used, moderate holster wear, ~150-200 rounds fired.
Custom cut compensation ports in slide and barrel - this type of mod usually calls for a "bull" type or "heavy" barrel but I just had the standard bushing barrel ported so there is a clearance between the barrel and the slide that collects carbon with heavy use. Sweet shooter, just need to fund another dream of mine.

I also have the original case as well as the factory mainspring housing with the safety lockout whizz-bang mechanism. Can also dig up the plastic holster and mag pouch if desired.
Asking $700
Willing to drive to sensible location for face to face.
